<p><strong>Test 914-1410</strong><br />
<strong>Name:</strong> Junior Researcher Collins<br />
<strong>Date:</strong> 29/01/2020<br />
<strong>Total Items:</strong> One Blu-Ray of Season 4 of the original Twilight Zone series.<br />
<strong>Input:</strong> Above item.<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Fine<br />
<strong>Output:</strong> One Blu-Ray of Season 914 of The Twilight Zone, containing 19 episodes of 914 themed cautionary tales. Rod Serling has been replaced by Dr. Veritas and each researcher plays themselves in dramatizations of previous test logs. However, the show is still in monochromatic film and the props/effects are seemingly from the same era. The episode list is as follows:</p>
<p>1. Site 19-23<br />
2. The Miracle of Loaves and Fish<br />
3. Biological Testing has been Discontinued<br />
4. The Man<br />
5. Paper Crane<br />
6. No Wife, No Life<br />
7. Заводной (Clockwork)<br />
8. Caution: Cognitohazard Detected<br />
