18. Memetic Madness<br />
19. 4.358 Squared</p>
<p><em>Note: Dr. Veritas if this clears anomalous screening could we put it in the break room? Also, a Rod Serling role surprisingly really suits you. – Junior Researcher Collins</em></p>
<p><em>Note: Provided it clears, granted. – Dr. Veritas</em></p>
<hr />
