<p><em>Note: SCP-914 has, in the past, shown the ability to reference events and people specific to the individual running the test at the time. This is nothing particularly new. I’m lucky it was only my hand. - Dr. Nightingale</em></p>
<p><strong>Input:</strong> One Foundation-issue prosthetic right hand.<br />
<strong>Setting:</strong> Fine<br />
