<p><em>Note: Recreating that scene from Evil Dead 2 was most certainly not on my to-do list for the very first test I conducted, but here we are. Aside from that last one, I’d judge this line of tests to be a relatively successful bunch. At least no one died, though that is not a very high bar to reach for, to be perfectly honest. - Dr. Nightingale</em></p>
